video_description: Are Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce dating? Neither the music icon nor the football player is saying anything about the chatter, but that's not stopping people from asking. Travis recently dodged questions about Taylor during an NFL+ interview after he previously admitted to his brother Jason on their podcast "New Heights" that he tried to give her his phone number on a friendship bracelet during her Eras Tour stop in Kansas City. I'm not gonna talk about my personal life. I know what you writers wanna hear, and you wanna hear more about that and I'm not gonna give you anything." The 33-year-old singer is presumably single at the moment but she was in a relationship with Joe Alwyn for six years until they split up in April. Taylor then dated the 1975's Matty Healy briefly until they parted ways in June.

video_title: Jackson Olson Accepts He Won't Date Taylor Swift Amid Travis Kelce Rumors
video_description: Savannah Bananas baseball player, Jackson Olson, has humorously conceded that his chances of dating pop sensation Taylor Swift are slim to none. This admission comes amidst swirling rumors of Taylor Swift's romantic involvement with NFL star Travis Kelce. In a TikTok video posted on September 13, the 25-year-old athlete lip-synced to Taylor's song "The 1" and expressed his realization, captioning it with, "When you had no chance with Taylor Swift but see she's dating Travis Kelce." On Instagram, he added, "Mr. Americana & The Heartbreak Princess," playfully acknowledging the situation.This lighthearted video has quickly gained popularity, amassing over 4.7 million views on TikTok and sparking numerous discussions on Instagram.Although neither Taylor Swift nor Travis Kelce, both aged 33, have publicly addressed the dating rumors, Travis did reveal his attempt to connect with the singer during her Eras Tour stop in Kansas City in July. Travis shared his disappointment at not being able to converse with Taylor before or after her shows due to her need to preserve her voice for her performances. He had hoped to gift her one of the bracelets he had made. Swifties, Taylor Swift's devoted fans, often exchange friendship bracelets, and Travis wanted to present her with one containing his contact information.The speculation about Travis and Taylor's relationship has left fans curious, especially since Taylor recently ended her six-year relationship with Joe Alwyn and briefly dated The 1975's Matty Healy.As for Jackson Olson, he's fully embraced his Swiftie era, from wearing 1989 merchandise to convincing his teammates to listen to Taylor's music. He even attended one of her concerts this summer, sharing videos of himself singing along to her songs in the crowd, all while humorously remarking, "When you're in your lover era at the T Swift concert, but you haven't found your wife yet."

When Travis Kelce scored his first touchdown of the season, the NFL announcer made a light-hearted reference to Taylor Swift.

When tight end Travis Kelce scored his first touchdown of the season in a recent NFL game, commentator Ian Eagle peppered his remarks with a little humor. To paraphrase Eagle's witty remark, "Kelce finds a blank space for the score," you can think of Taylor Swift's hit "Blank Space." Given the persistent rumors that Kelce is spending time with the internationally renowned pop singer, Taylor Swift, this humorous remark has sparked quite the buzz.

Though neither Swift nor Kelce, who are both 33 years old, have commented publicly on the dating allegations, sources close to the couple have intimated that they have been spending time together behind closed doors. Swift's recent visit to Kelce in Nashville adds fuel to the fire surrounding their rumored romance.

Travis Kelce and his brother Jason Kelce, who co-hosts the "New Heights" podcast with him, have remained unusually quiet about the subject despite widespread interest and speculation. When Jason asked Travis about his new mustache and whether he had found Taylor Swift's opinion on it, Travis cut him off, saying, "We are not bringing up Taylor Swift in this episode."

The significance of this podcast exchange stems from Travis Kelce's earlier sadness over not being able to give Taylor Swift a friendship bracelet bearing his phone number during one of her performances earlier in the summer. Since Swift saves her voice for her demanding performances, he feels she could do more to communicate with her fans.

Fans and the media are keeping a close eye on Travis Kelce and Taylor Swift because of the ongoing relationship allegations. Fans are eagerly anticipating official confirmation of the relationship, but the couple has yet to address the speculation over whether or not they are dating.

The intriguing crossover of sports and entertainment in today's celebrity-driven culture is on full display in this developing story between the NFL great and the music superstar. Whether or whether they are dating, the public's fascination with the pair's interactions remains undimmed.

video_title: Dave Portnoy: Travis Kelce is using Taylor Swift dating rumors ‚Äòfor clout‚Äô
video_description:
Dave Portnoy believes Travis Kelce is playing into romance rumors with Taylor Swift for his personal benefit.

The Barstool Sports founder re-posted a blog post from his employee and ‚ÄúSwiftie‚Äù Kelly Keegs that was titled, ‚ÄúI Now Think Travis Kelce Is Using Taylor Swift For Clout.‚Äù

‚ÄúYou know what? I ride with Keegs on this one. I Think Travis Kelce Is Using Taylor Swift For Clout,‚Äù he tweeted on Tuesday.

Portnoy, 46, shared his opinion just one night before Travis‚Äô brother, Jason Kelce, joked about whether the ‚ÄúCruel Summer‚Äù singer and the Kansas City Chiefs player are romantically involved.

‚ÄúIt‚Äôs hard to answer because I don‚Äôt really know what‚Äôs happening with Travis‚Äô love life,‚Äù Jason said during his interview with radio station 94WIP Wednesday when asked about the speculation.

However, the Philadelphia Eagles athlete, 35, then divulged, ‚ÄúBut having said that, I think they‚Äôre doing great and I think it‚Äôs all 100 percent true.‚Äù

He then clarified, ‚ÄúNo I‚Äôm joking. I don‚Äôt even know what‚Äôs happening.‚Äù

Swift and Travis, both 33, have been reportedly hanging out for a few weeks after the NFL champ tried ‚Äì but failed ‚Äì to give the pop star his phone number at one of her Eras Tour concerts in July.

A source then told the Messenger that the two were ‚Äúquietly hanging out,‚Äù but both A-listers have not directly addressed their relationship status.

However, Travis laughed off some of the cheeky chatter on Sunday via Instagram.

After Jason spoke out about the rumored romance, Portnoy doubled down, tweeting Wednesday, ‚ÄúAgain side with Keegs. Im sick and tired of the Kelce brothers.

He also added that he didn‚Äôt want to give the brothers ‚Äúattention that they don‚Äôt deserve.‚Äù

Portnoy has been very vocal about the fact that he would not pick Travis to date Swift.

‚ÄúWouldn‚Äôt be my 1st choice but Mother works hard to provide for us,‚Äù he wrote on his Instagram Story last week. ‚ÄúShe is allowed to have fun too.‚Äù

However, the social media personality then wrote that he ‚Äúthink[s]‚Äù he approves of the rumored romance after all, but he‚Äôs still hesitant because Travis is a ‚Äúhuge spotlight guy.‚Äù

‚ÄúSo I bet he likes the idea of dating Taylor more than actually dating her,‚Äù Portnoy wrote on a Sept. 12 Barstool blog. ‚ÄúBut that‚Äôs okay. Taylor loves dating big-name celebs who are sure to break her heart so why not a football player over some DJ or musician?‚Äù

The famed pizza reviewer candidly added that ‚Äúthere is no shot in hell this relationship works,‚Äù but ‚Äúat the very least we should get a few good songs out of the break up.‚Äù

video_description:
Taylor Swift responds to Travis Kelce dating rumors.
Fans are speculating if Taylor Swift responded to the Travis Kelce dating rumors by wearing an opal necklace on an outing in New York. It sounds benign, but Swifties were, ahem, swift, to point out that opal is the October birthstone and Kelce‚Äôs birthday is October 5. ‚ÄúKelce is a libra and opal is our birthstone,‚Äù one eagle-eyed Swiftie commented on @taylorswiftstyled‚Äôs Instagram post spotlighting the star‚Äôs jewelry; ‚ÄúI‚Äôve put my [clown emoji] makeup on and I‚Äôm listening,‚Äù another joked in response. ‚Äúeven though i believe the kelce‚Äôs [sic] started the dating rumor to promote their documentary‚Ä¶ opal is october birthstone and travis was born in october,‚Äù another pointed out. The tear-drop-shaped pendant is part of a necklace Foundrae‚Äôs Forever & Always a Pair Pendant ($1,150), described by the website as representing love. ‚ÄúEach pair comes at a time in our lives when something just feels right. These pairs of pears, we absorb them, fuse them into our own hearts, and our heart grows as a result. It‚Äôs those pairs we choose to keep; friends, lovers, family, chosen family, a part of our heart forever. Forever and always, perpetually, and unceasingly bound.‚Äù The rumors of Kelce and Swift seemed to solidify when The Messenger reported that ‚ÄúTaylor and Travis have been quietly hanging out,‚Äù according to a source who spoke to the outlet. ‚ÄúShe saw him when she was in NYC a few weeks ago,‚Äù the insider said.  According to sources who spoke to ET, however, the pair aren‚Äôt actually an item‚Äîbut that doesn‚Äôt mean there aren‚Äôt any feelings involved. A source told ET, ‚ÄúTravis has been into Taylor for a while and definitely has a crush on her. He is a simple guy that is very funny, charismatic, chill, and loves playing football.‚Äù

 On Sunday, September 17, 2023, NFL announcers were having a field day with the jokes and it sounds like he‚Äôs taking it all in stride. When Kelce scored a touchdown against the Jacksonville Jaguars, commentator Ian Eagle quipped, ‚ÄúKelce finds a blank space for the score,‚Äù making reference to Swift‚Äôs song ‚ÄúBlank Space‚Äù from her 1989 album, adding later that the champion tight end could ‚Äúshake it off‚Äù after suffering a knee injury in practice a few weeks prior, another reference to a T-Swift song, ‚ÄúShake It Off‚Äù.

NFL Network‚Äôs Rich Eisen chimed in with the banter on Twitter with a rollcall of Swift hits while covering Kelce‚Äôs return to the field, including ‚ÄúDelicate,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnti-Hero‚Äù and ‚ÄúAugust.‚Äù Sharing a clip of the broadcast via Instagram, Eisen wrote in the caption, ‚ÄúLook what you made me do, @killatrav.‚Äù Kelce responded: ‚ÄúWell played Rich‚Ä¶ Well played." Two months prior, Kelce seemingly opened up about his crush on the singer during an episode of the podcast ‚ÄúNew Heights,‚Äù in which he revealed that he tried to give her a friendship bracelet with his phone number on it before one of her concerts for her Eras Tour at Arrowhead Stadium in Kansas City. ‚ÄúI was disappointed that she doesn‚Äôt talk before or after her shows because she has to save her voice for the 44 songs that she sings, so I was a little butthurt I didn‚Äôt get to hand her one of the bracelets I made for her,‚Äù he admitted at the time. The football player‚Äôs brother, Jason Kelce, had a funny theory as to why Taylor didn‚Äôt end up meeting them that night: ‚ÄúShe probably just hasn‚Äôt gotten over the Super Bowl yet,‚Äù Jason joked. ‚ÄúShe‚Äôs a big Eagles fan, so maybe she just made something up and didn‚Äôt want to talk to you,‚Äù to which Travis quipped, ‚ÄúDammit!‚Äù

Taylor Swift Subtly Responded To Those Travis Kelce Dating Rumors.

When dating rumors begin to swirl, fans will look for any sign of confirmation. And if you know anything about birthstones, you might take this news as Taylor Swift responding to those Travis Kelce rumors.

The NFL player was asked about his rumored relationship with the singer during an appearance on NFL+ with host Andrew Siciliano after reports that he once tried to give the ‚ÄúLavender Haze‚Äù singer his phone number earlier this year at one of her concerts. ‚ÄúThe only thing anyone really wants to talk about is Taylor Swift,‚Äù Siciliano said in the interview, a clip from which has since been reshared on TikTok. ‚ÄúDid you really have your phone number ready on a friendship bracelet to give to Taylor?‚Äù  Kelce seemingly confirmed that the reports about trying to give his number to Taylor were true. ‚ÄúI said what I said. And I meant what I said when I said it. And you know what, it is what it is,‚Äù he said, before playing it coy about their relationship status. ‚ÄúI‚Äôm not gonna talk about my personal life,‚Äù he added.

The Kansas City Chiefs tight end went on to playfully tease listeners. ‚ÄúI know what you writers wanna hear, and you wanna hear more about that and I‚Äôm not gonna give you anything,‚Äù he joked while pointing a finger at the camera. Siciliano pressed him for more, however. ‚ÄúHas she reached out?‚Äù he asked, to which Travis remained tight-lipped. ‚ÄúAnd that‚Äôs gonna wrap it up here,‚Äù he said, ending the interview.

With dating rumors swirling around NFL star Travis Kelce and pop star Taylor Swift, Kelce reveals some dealbreakers.

Relationship Preferences and Philosophy of a Kansas City Chiefs Player
In light of the persistent speculation that NFL star Travis Kelce is dating Taylor Swift, the Kansas City Chiefs tight end discussed his relationship preferences and dealbreakers on Kristin Cavallari's podcast, "Let's Be Honest."
Kelce, in the podcast episode, discussed his preference for low-key companions and the difficulties he has with "high-maintenance" people. For him, the biggest turnoff is someone who is arrogant or who has an inflated sense of self-importance: "If you're arrogant or you think you're snooty or higher or above people, that's the biggest turnoff for me."
Kelce, 33, also said that he hopes to find in a partner the attributes that made his mother, Donna Kelce, "an absolute angel." Kindness and tenderness are qualities that he thinks are crucial in a life mate.
Kelce mentioned in a recent interview that he takes his time getting to know people and does not fall in love easily. True feelings of love and affection, he said, take a lot of time to develop. Kelce believes that meeting the perfect person and developing a committed relationship takes time, and he is not one to rush into anything.
Kelce is patient when it comes to love because he knows "the stars will align" when he meets the right person, despite the persistent rumors that he is dating Taylor Swift.
During one of Swift's Eras Tour gigs, Kelce allegedly tried to offer her his phone number, sparking speculation about their possible relationship. Despite rumors that Kelce and Swift have been "hanging out" for weeks, neither one of them has commented publicly on their relationship status.
In a recent "Thursday Night Football" appearance, Jason Kelce, older brother of the player in question, addressed the claims, saying that Travis was "just having fun" with all of the attention. Earlier this month, Swift was spotted wearing an opal necklace, which happens to be the birthstone of Travis Kelce, a Libra.

Jason Kelce Jokingly Addresses the Dating Rumors Between Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce

While rumors of a romance between pop star Taylor Swift and Kansas City Chiefs' star tight end Travis Kelce persist, Travis's brother Jason Kelce, a center for the Philadelphia Eagles, recently added some comic relief to the rumors during an interview on the "WIP Morning Show."
When asked about his brother's sexual life, 35-year-old Jason admitted he was taken aback by the queries. He was emphasizing that he doesn't generally interfere in his brother's personal affairs.
His comments were taken seriously at first, but he quickly said, "No, I'm joking. I have no idea what is going on.
There was a lot of buzz regarding Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce having a love relationship when rumors spread that they had been "quietly hanging out." When Travis made an apparent attempt to give Swift his number during one of her recent Eras Tour shows, it became clear that they may have already met.
Swift and Kelce haven't come out and said they're dating, but there have been clues that they might be. While the NFL star has joked about the rumors, Taylor Swift has been seen wearing a necklace with Travis's birthstone.
Recently, photos emerged of Taylor Swift and her pal Sophie Turner having a good time on the town. Joe Jonas' ex-girlfriends are Turner and Swift. The two famous people were spotted leaving the hip Italian restaurant Via Carota in New York City arm-in-arm after having dinner there.
Representatives for both Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce have remained mum about the relationship rumors as of yet.

Dave Portnoy's Claims About a Romance Between Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce Cause Confusion Kelce Wants Power

Jason Kelce Makes a Joke Regarding the Dating Rumors, At the Same Time That Travis Kelce Is Using Taylor Swift for Publicity, Dave Portnoy
Founder of Barstool Sports Dave Portnoy has made headlines by accusing NFL star Travis Kelce of trying to boost his reputation by being linked to Taylor Swift.
The rumors that Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce are dating have been a hot topic ever since Kelce reportedly tried to offer Swift his phone number at one of Swift's shows. The speculations have persisted despite the fact that neither party has commented publicly on the nature of their connection.
Dave Portnoy chimed in by sharing an internal blog entry written by one of his workers, Kelly Keegs, headlined "I Now Think Travis Kelce Is Using Taylor Swift For Clout." As an expression of his agreement, Portnoy tweeted, "You know what? On this one, I'm in Keegs' camp. Travis Kelce, in my opinion, is using Taylor Swift as a form of influence.
A day before this scandal emerged, Travis Kelce's brother, Philadelphia Eagles player Jason Kelce, made light of the dating rumors in an interview with 94WIP. In response to inquiries regarding the rumors, Jason pretended at first to be oblivious to Travis's romantic status, saying, "It's hard to answer because I don't really know what's happening with Travis' love life."
Jokingly, he continued, "But having said that, I think they're doing great, and I think it's all 100 percent true." After being asked if he was serious, Jason said, "No, I'm joking. I have no idea what is going on.
Travis Kelce responded with a hilarious Instagram video, but he still didn't address the rumors of a romance between himself and Taylor Swift head-on.
By tweeting, "Again side with Keegs. ", Dave Portnoy made it clear that he did not approve of the Kelce brothers' actions. When asked about the Kelce brothers, he said, "I'm sick and tired of them," before adding, "I don't want to give them attention that they don't deserve."
Despite previously saying that Travis Kelce isn't his first pick to date Taylor Swift, Portnoy now seems to cautiously approve of the potential romance, saying that Travis is a "huge spotlight guy." He anticipated that the relationship would fail, but that it could lead to some hit songs if Travis was inspired to write them about their time together.
Fans are waiting impatiently for Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce to address the rumors and controversy surrounding their relationship.

video_title: Travis Kelce Went From A Broke IG Model To @TaylorSwift And GUESS WHO MAD?
video_description:
Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce are officially spending time together!

The "Lavender Haze" singer, 33, was captured on video leaving Arrowhead Stadium in Kansas City, Missouri, on Sunday night with the Kansas City Chiefs tight end, also 33, by her side.

As the two walked together other on their way out of the building, Swift smiled briefly at the camera and appeared to say "bye." Kelce, dressed in a patterned two-piece outfit, also shot a smile and brief nod to the camera.


Swift was part of the crowd cheering on the Chiefs in their matchup against the Chicago Bears Sunday. She watched the on-field action from Kelce's suite with the athlete's mother, Donna Kelce. The pair could be seen sitting shoulder-to-shoulder and chatting and laughing together throughout the game.
The Grammy winner showed her team spirit by wearing a red-and-white Chiefs jacket, which was later tied around her waist as she left the stadium. Footage from the game, shared by Fox Sports on X, showed Swift smiling, cheering and clapping enthusiastically as she watched Kelce and his teammates. At one point, she even raised her hands in the air in excitement.

Swift's stadium appearance comes just days after Kelce invited her to attend the game while appearing on The Pat McAfee Show podcast. A source told PEOPLE that once Swift heard about the invite, she didn't let a busy schedule stop her from accepting.

video_title: Taylor Swift sparks dating rumours with Travis Kelce after attending football game
video_description:
Taylor Swift is sparking dating rumours with NFL star Travis Kelce after she attended the Kansas City Chief football game against the Chicago Bears on Sunday.

The Grammy award winner was seen with Kelce's mother in a private box, wearing the team's red and white colours to support her rumoured new boyfriend. 

Kelce said this week on ESPN's Pat McAfee Show that he had invited Swift to a game after he attended her Eras tour back in July.

"I threw it out there. I threw the ball in her court. You know, I told her, 'I've seen you rock the stage in Arrowhead, you might have to come see me rock the stage in Arrowhead and see which one's a little more lit,'" he said.

The 'Lover' singer reportedly broke up with her long-term boyfriend, Joe Alwyn, in April.
